Sure. It's five eight two seven four one.
Great, thank you. Now, could you also confirm your date of birth?
Of course. It's zero nine one four one nine eight zero.
Thank you for providing the information, Patricia. How can I assist you today with your Old Stone Auto Insurance policy?
I need to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can help you with that. Please provide me with the make, model, and year of the vehicle you'd like to add.
Thank you. It's a Honda Civic, two zero zero eight.
Thank you, Patricia, for the details. I will update your policy to include the Honda Civic. Is there anything else you need assistance with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Daniel, for your help.
You're welcome, Patricia. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
